The image description is available below each image.

Image 1:
This image displays an open web browser window with a JavaScript code highlighted in yellow. The code is about a "send" and "receive" data via AJAX and XML. It also includes some information about images and videos.

JavaScript Code:
```javascript
// XMLHttpRequest object
var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();

// set up the XMLHttpRequest object
xhr.open("POST", "process.php", true);
xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {
    if (this.readyState == 4 && this.status == 200) {
        // handle the response
        var data = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
        // do something with the data
        console.log(data);
    }
};

// send the request to the server
xhr.send("name=John&age=30");
```
